tic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/d859a9c153188559cf0d4e44756600db.avif?t=1694182159\" width=526 height=324 /></span><br><br><strong>How to play...</strong><br><br><strong><i>Combat system</i></strong><br><br>Classic turn-based combat <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/d308b4ab388b6e4fbd365a393c81cadd.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span> just like old good times Rogue. Move towards your enemy and push! the turn resolution will show up just after you hit. Be careful to not to hurry, or you'll not be fast enough to anticipate your next move...<br><br><strong><i>Levelling up</i></strong><br><br>Rogue Valley levelling system is a bit different than others. Kill monsters in the dungeon so you can learn their abilities, earn stat points depending on the monster you're eliminating. It gets more difficult as you kill... <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/7fc4c974cbc9786f768d222a67482fb8.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><br><br><strong><i>Rogue Valley world</i></strong><br><br>You thought you've reached every map corner? maybe not... <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/58631ffb16b5efa636e20b669bdc8d39.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span> dungeons refresh and regenerate randomly from time to time and as every game season passes. The dungeon is alive!<br><br><strong><i>Go deeper, with friends</i></strong><br><br>New floors every season, <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/d3cc32970017693733e7cd0b04e8ec72.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span> explore and evolve along with friends. Is there a strong monster down there? don't go alone! you can help killing monsters and share the loot.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/da1148a73bc76006aef3ae28a264f2d5.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>Come play with us!</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/6dac49084df33b85863a608af07e4823.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/4b53d927146fcb4d21557b65a84d8c25.avif?t=1694182159\" width=160 height=80 /></span><br>Immerse in a classic <strong>90's rogue-like</strong> adventure <strong>with friends</strong>!<br><br>Join Rogue Valley, a MMO rogue-like world and explore the different dungeon levels each season along with your friends. Collect items and improve your character without limits. Our unique level-up system is focused on farming and exploring to find new challenges, earning points for your character naturally rather than having a static experience/level system.<br><br><strong>This is not a pay-to-win game</strong>! so we don't have an in-game shop, we prefer to sell you the full game directly and give you the whole experience while we grow together in this online world in order to maintain and keep our servers active for you.<br><br>We're in early access stage, so we'll actively be enhancing your gameplay experience!<br>Thank you for playing with us :)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"b