m/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/13e3aac84f39c651668dab167259d969.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/d859a9c153188559cf0d4e44756600db.avif?t=1694182159\" width=526 height=324 /></span><br><br><strong>How to play...</strong><br><br><strong><i>Combat system</i></strong><br><br>Classic turn-based combat <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/d308b4ab388b6e4fbd365a393c81cadd.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span> just like old good times Rogue. Move towards your enemy and push! the turn resolution will show up just after you hit. Be careful to not to hurry, or you'll not be fast enough to anticipate your next move...<br><br><strong><i>Levelling up</i></strong><br><br>Rogue Valley levelling system is a bit different than others. Kill monsters in the dungeon so you can learn their abilities, earn stat points depending on the monster you're eliminating. It gets more difficult as you kill... <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/7fc4c974cbc9786f768d222a67482fb8.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span><br><br><strong><i>Rogue Valley world</i></strong><br><br>You thought you've reached every map corner? maybe not... <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/58631ffb16b5efa636e20b669bdc8d39.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span> dungeons refresh and regenerate randomly from time to time and as every game season passes. The dungeon is alive!<br><br><strong><i>Go deeper, with friends</i></strong><br><br>New floors every season, <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/d3cc32970017693733e7cd0b04e8ec72.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span> explore and evolve along with friends. Is there a strong monster down there? don't go alone! you can help killing monsters and share the loot.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/da1148a73bc76006aef3ae28a264f2d5.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>Come play with us!</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202760/extras/6dac49084df33b85863a608af07e4823.webp?t=1694182159\" width=16 height=16 /></span>",
